{"id":123625,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/音频：律师谈无法见到赵连海/","date":"2010-11-19T04:28:34Z","modified":"2010-11-19T04:28:34Z","title":"音频：律师谈无法见到赵连海","content":"<div>\n<p>以寻衅滋事罪被判刑两年半的中国毒奶粉受害儿童家长赵连海的律师李方平和彭剑前往看守所会见赵连海时再次遭到拒绝。</p>\n<p>BBC中文网在两位律师刚刚离开大兴看守所时对他们进行了电话采访。</p>\n<p>李方平说，看守所警方向他们出示了一张据说是赵连海亲笔书写的条子，声称他不想会见律师。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/lEaIv3_IGv289vrV7nCEoM7vx_E/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/lEaIv3_IGv289vrV7nCEoM7vx_E/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/lEaIv3_IGv289vrV7nCEoM7vx_E/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/lEaIv3_IGv289vrV7nCEoM7vx_E/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=eD2nlX6MBiU:xFbTqbTVEMc:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=eD2nlX6MBiU:xFbTqbTVEMc:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=eD2nlX6MBiU:xFbTqbTVEMc:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=eD2nlX6MBiU:xFbTqbTVEMc:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=eD2nlX6MBiU:xFbTqbTVEMc:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=eD2nlX6MBiU:xFbTqbTVEMc:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/eD2nlX6MBiU\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/multim